{"tid":2289630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"副局長入市｜廖振新施政報告前2,335萬買銀湖‧天峰　低估價20%","createTime":"2020-11-17T11:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T12:02:20.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5636afa5162d5f713faf7737b5148b16bc6e14f6","tid":2289630,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IwXDsrxbhqk5pjZfHSm9J8GcyUI=/1600x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DTDUGJNP6FHT7D2FXKEMBIN6TA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIwXDsrxbhqk5pjZfHSm9J8GcyUI%3D%2F1600x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDTDUGJNP6FHT7D2FXKEMBIN6TA.jpeg&h=82157923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發展局副局長廖振新低價買入的銀湖‧天峰四房單位，客廳外望海景。<br />\n...<br />\n施政報告下周三公佈前夕，樓市現政府高官低價入市。土地註冊處料顯示，馬鞍山銀湖‧天峰6座10樓B室，實用面積1,856方呎，屬4房單位，成交價2,335萬元，呎價僅12,581元，比銀行估值大幅低兩成。登記新買家為廖振新（LIU CHUN SAN），與現任發展局副局長同名。<br />\n翻查官員利益申請資料，發展局局長辦公室於11月2日，按廖振新通知申報擁有沙田區一層的自住住宅樓宇，料為上述銀湖‧天峰新購物業。查冊顯示，有關物業於上月28日簽定臨時買賣合約。而據利益申報，廖振新在購入銀湖‧天峰單位前，本港未見有任何物業，故是次料以首置身份入市，只需支付樓價4.25%最低稅率，涉及稅款約99萬元。至於其妻鄭嬋珠，除了在內地東莞持有一個自住單位外，並在2018年申報購入沙田區一個自住單位，即兩人在短短兩年間兩度入市，相當看好香港樓市。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201117/XSBE5EVZVBHWDEOIUOHBP7ULOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201117%2FXSBE5EVZVBHWDEOIUOHBP7ULOA%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM41T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=60144628\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201117%2FXSBE5EVZVBHWDEOIUOHBP7ULOA%2F&h=61daab37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201117/XSBE5EVZVBHWDEOIUOHBP7ULOA/</a>"},{"pid":"ea8477b0ba98daedd30d837c26dafe03f7fa18df","tid":2289630,"uid":179729,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"千八呎都幾大，唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e06d187b5666b3f7828c442ecdb6c43a04a06aa","tid":2289630,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/228693/發展局副局長持新界農地%E3%80%80或引利益衝突問題/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F228693%2F%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%B1%80%E5%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E6%8C%81%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E8%BE%B2%E5%9C%B0%25E3%2580%2580%E6%88%96%E5%BC%95%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM41T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=a70847e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/228693/發展局副局長持新界農地%E3%80%80或引利益衝突問題/</a><br />\n<br />\n原來係地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正一漢奸走狗賣國賊"},{"pid":"20bb5a779da52903d14316c5cc918f269bc2c168","tid":2289630,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"梁錦松：<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b74ff1ae0e54d999ca145b5546bb44796fe01b","tid":2289630,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"阿松當年真係慘"},{"pid":"a81e579f68e14714ae15ae4d4f9dfb96e2ea5e3e","tid":2289630,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"腐敗地主<br />\n危害國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd175ef2f93ddb69c93f1263d328ac3e47fec61f","tid":2289630,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"朱門酒肉臭"}]}